Serie Information
=================

This windows allows to select the serie of the current album. If a serie doesn't exist, it could be created in this window.

$wizard.img$

Name
...

* Serie's name.
* This field is compulsory.

Type
....

* Type of the serie.
* Select one among those proposed, or create a new one by entering it's name.

One shot
........

* Click on the box if the serie is a one shot.

Description
...........

* Description relative to the serie.


